(204, 'Alvin', 'Kanak', NULL, 'Alvin Kanak was commissioned to do the Inukshuk in Vancouver because of his skill as a carver recommended by the people in his community.  He is also a hunter, fisher,and  trapper, and has eight children.', 'https://covapp.vancouver.ca/PublicArtRegistry/ArtistDetail.aspx?FromArtistIndex=False&ArtistId=211', NULL, 2),
