(140, 'Fisherman (Hauling in the Net)', 'In Place', '1976-01-01', 'VanDusen Botanical Garden', ' 5251 Oak Street', 'This fisherman, modeled in clay and then cast in bronze, stuggles to pull in a non-existing net heavy with imaginary fish from the pond beside which he is situated.', NULL, '49.239145', '-123.129578', 'Bronze', 'https://covapp.vancouver.ca/PublicArtRegistry/ImageDisplay.aspx?AreaId=155&ImageId=771', 'https://covapp.vancouver.ca/PublicArtRegistry/ArtworkDetail.aspx?ArtworkId=155', 9, 1, 8),
